                    for small to medium sized plants in the home. The smaller load cell provides more sensitivity, allowing +/-1g readings.
                </p>
                <p>
                    This device can be used to monitor cut flowers or a fermentation. Cut flowers 
                    will change their water use rate as the stems become blocked by bacteria. 
                    Fermentations can be monitored by mass because when bubbles of carbon dioxide leave the fermentation mass is reduced.
                </p>
